text=(:if [ authgroup @tas || authgroup @admins || equal {$Author} '' ]:)%0a%0a(:toggle id=gi show="show grading interface" hide="hide grading interface":)%0a%0a>>id=gi%3c%3c%0a%0a[[GradebookArticles.{$Name}|See article in gradebook]] \\%0a[[{$FullName}?action=diff|See all changes to article]] \\%0a[[{$FullName}?action=edit|Edit this page]] \\%0aStatus: {GradebookArticles.{$Name}$:Status} %0a%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradeitem:)%0a%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#gradingcomment:)%0a%0a>>%3c%3c%0a%0a----%0a%0a(:ifend:)%0a%0a[[!{$:Category}]]%0a%0a!Copium%0a%0a:Author: serenali%0a%0a'''Summary:''' \\%0a%0a[[#summary]]%0a%0aWhy "Copium" should be added to OED%0a%0a[[#summaryends]]%0a%0a----%0a[[#content]]%0a%0aCopium is a combination of cope and opium. It is more commonly used to describe a person "lying to [themselves] in order to cope with something" or to cope with loss(1). It is commonly expressed in memes when someone lies about their performance in order to feel better about themselves. The usage of the words is starting to become widespread as it is listed on wikipedia, urban dictionary, and have articles talking about it.%0a%0aThe earliest known usage of "'Copium' was in 2003 when Keak da Sneak released the album "Copium" in the US." (3) The word's existence on the web began in 2018 when it gained popularity on Twitch(3). The word started off as an emote on Reddit and Twitch. However, "Copium" has a presence outside of Twitch's platform, having massive popularity in political memes during the 2016 election.%0a%0aThe word's relevancy cannot be diminished since every conflict within sports, video games, or political group has shown a resurgence of the word "Copium", exploding in popularity in 2003, 2016, and 2018(2). Now, when "Copium" is searched in 2022, there are myriads of articles explaining the definition of "Copium" as well as having its own Wiki page and urban dictionary definition. The resurgence of "Copium" should not be ignored, and should become a part of the Oxford English Dictionary. %0a%0aReferences:%0a(1) https://www.urbandictionary.com/define.php?term=Copium%0a(2) https://gamertweak.com/twitch-copium-meme-meaning/%0a(3) https://afkgaming.com/esports/news/7410-what-does-copium-mean-in-twitch-chat-and-where-did-it-originate%0a%0a[[#contentends]]%0a----%0a----%0a%0a!!Expansions:%0a[[#expansions]]%0a%0a[[#expansionsend]]%0a%0a----%0a%25red%25 '''Add an expansion:'''%0a%0a(:if [ exists GradebookExpansions.{$Name}-{$Author} || equal {$Author} {$:Author} ] :)%0a%0a(:elseif [ equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:andrewid} '' || equal {Profiles.{$Author}$:section} '' ] :)%0a%0aYou must enter your andrew ID and section before submitting an expansion. %0a%0a(:else:)%0a%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#newexpansion:)%0a%0a(:ifend:)%0a%0a----%0a----%0a%0a!!Comments%0a%0a%0a%0a%0a----%0a(:if equal {$Author} {$:Author}:)%0a!!Change article category%0a(:foxform Site.FoxForms#changearticlecategory:)%0a(:ifend:)%0a%0a%0a(:Section: A:)%0a(:Category: FunWithWords:)%0a(:Title: Copium:)
